Package gov.sandia.gmp.util.containers.tree

Class TreeIntrinsic

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.gmp.util.containers.tree.TreeIntrinsic
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
TreeMapDoubleDouble, TreeMapDoubleFloat, TreeMapDoubleInteger, TreeMapDoubleKey, TreeMapDoubleLong, TreeMapFloatDouble, TreeMapFloatFloat, TreeMapFloatInteger, TreeMapFloatKey, TreeMapFloatLong, TreeMapIntegerDouble, TreeMapIntegerFloat, TreeMapIntegerInteger, TreeMapIntegerKey, TreeMapIntegerLong, TreeMapLongDouble, TreeMapLongFloat, TreeMapLongInteger, TreeMapLongKey, TreeMapLongLong, TreeSetDouble, TreeSetFloat, TreeSetInteger, TreeSetLong
public abstract class TreeIntrinsic extends Object implements Serializable
The base class used by all intrinsic Tree sets and maps. Most of the tree-traversal mechanics are defined here. The key and value operations are defined in all derived classes.
